T1  - Dynamics of imitation versus innovation in technological leadership change: Latecomers’ catch-up strategies in diverse technological regimes
AU  - Chang, Sungyong
AU  - Kim, Hyunseob
AU  - Song, Jaeyong
AU  - Lee, Keun
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 53
